  "text": "The paper most related to ours is [CITATION_1] , which presents a model to maximize the revenue from the liquidation of a single product across a retail chain. A central planner sets a constant price across all stores, and inventory may be transferred among stores. The authors examine the efficacy of their model using a simulation based on data from a Chilean retail chain.",
